title_full:
Princess Diana of Wales

            —
            Still Beach

label: Incienso
description:
Marco Shuttle saddles up a trip to mystic, offbeat zones between the chill out room and desert of the mind for Anthony Naples & Jenny Slattery’s Incienso.

With nary a conventional 4/4 groove in earshot, Shuttle works in a fractal not fractional groove on 11 tracks that really find their place amid Incienso’s roster of swangers and shufflers inc DJ Python and... more

label: STROOM
description:
Haunting Lithuanian folk songs and choral works from Merope, latest lambs to the Stroom flock shepherded by Ziggy Devriendt aka Nosedrip, a big big tip to fans of Kara-Lis Coverdale.

Immediately calling to mind strains of the Fonal label circa the mid ‘00s (Islaja, Paavoharju, et al), and likewise lilting, worldly traces of the label’s NSRD/Hardijs Lediņš... more

title_full:
Serafina Steer / John T. Gast

label: 5 Gate Temple
description:
Harpist Serafina Steer joins new age anachronism John T. Gast on pair of floatation tank specials
